quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Ndithudi tidatumiza Nowa kwa anthu ake: “Chenjeza anthu ako chilango chowawa chisadafike pa iwo.”"
  71,2,"Iye adati: “oh inu anthu anga! Ndithudi ine, ndine Mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu.”"
  71,3,“Kuti muzipembedza Mulungu ndi kumuopa Iye ndipo mundimvere ine.”
  71,4,"“Iye adzakukhululukirani machimo anu ndi kukusungani bwino mpaka nthawi ya imfa yanu. Ndithudi nthawi ya Mulungu ikakwana, palibe wina aliyense amene angaibwezere m’mbuyo inu mukadadziwa.”"
  71,5,"Iye adati: “oh Ambuye! Ndithudi usana ndi usiku ndakhala ndiri kuwaitana anthu anga.”"
  71,6,“Koma kuitana kwanga kwangoonjezera kusamvera kwawo.”
  71,7,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, nthawi yonse imene ndiitana kuti Inu muwakhululukire, iwo amatenga zala zawo ndi kutseka m’makutu mwawo ndipo amatenga mikhanjo yawo ndi kufunditsa kumutu kwawo ndipo amapitirirabe kuchita zoipa monyada.”"
  71,8,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, ine ndidalalikira mokweza kwa iwo.”"
  71,9,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, ndidawalankhula pagulu ndi mwamseri.”"
  71,10,"Ndidawauza: “Funsani chikhululukiro cha Ambuye wanu. Ndithudi Iye amakhululukira nthawi zonse.”"
  71,11,"“Iye adzakutumizirani Nuh\t621 mvula yochuluka.”"
  71,12,"“Ndikukupatsani inu chuma, ana, minda ndi mitsinje.”"
  71,13,"Kodi mwatani, inu simuyembekeza mphotho"
  71,14,Pamene Iye adakulengani inu m’nthawi zosiyana siyana
  71,15,"Kodi inu simuona mmene Mulungu adalengera miyamba isanu ndi iwiri, wina pamwamba pa unzake"
  71,16,Ndipo anapanga mwezi ngati muuni ndi dzuwa ngati nyali
  71,17,Mulungu adakulengani inu kuchokera ku nthaka
  71,18,Ndipo ku nthaka komweko adzakubwezerani inu ndi kukudzutsaninso
  71,19,Ndipo Mulungu adalenga dziko kukhala lalikulu kwa inu
  71,20,Kuti muziyenda m’njira zambiri za zikuluzikulu
  71,21,"Nowa adati: “oh Ambuye! Anthu anga sali kundimvera ine koma mmalo mwake ali kutsatira amene sangawaonjezere chuma ndi ana koma mavuto.”"
  71,22,Ndipo iwo akonza chiwembu champhamvu
  71,23,"Ndipo ati: “Mwanjira ina iliyonse inu musaleke kupembedza milungu yanu. Musaleke kupembedza Wadd, Suwa, Yaghuth, Yauq kapena Nasr.”"
  71,24,"“Ndipo, ndithudi, iwo asocheza anthu ambiri. Ndipo Inu musaonjeze china chili chonse kwa anthu ochita zoipa chifukwa apitirizabe kuchita zoipa.”"
  71,25,"Chifukwa cha machimo awo iwo anamizidwa ndipo adaponyedwa ku moto ndipo iwo sanapeze wina aliyense kuti awathandize, m’malo mwa Mulungu"
  71,26,"Ndipo Nowa adati: Ambuye wanga! Musasiye munthu aliyense padziko lapansi mwa anthu osakhulupirira"
  71,27,“Ngati Inu muwasiya iwo adzasocheretsa akapolo anu okhulupirira ndipo iwo adzabereka anthu ochita zoipa ndi osakhulupirira.”
  71,28,"“Ambuye wanga! Ndikhululukireni ine ndi makolo anga ndi iye amene alowa mnyumba yanga ngati wokhulupirira ndiponso okhulupirira onse amuna ndi akazi. Ndipo kwa anthu osakhulupilira, Inu musawaonjezere china koma chionongeko"